Sears , Orchard Supply deal clears hurdle . Sears , Roebuck and Co said Monday the Hart - Scott - Rodino antitrust waiting period had expired for its planned acquisition of Orchard Supply Hardware Stores Corp . About 1 . 1 million shares of common stock of Orchard were tendered as of September 6 , 1996 , pursuant . In August , Sears offered $ 35 for each share of San Jose , California - based Orchard , which operates 61 medium - sized hardware stores . - - Reuters Chicago newsdesk , 312 - 408 - 8787 
